WhiteFox::

She woke up and stretched. Yawning and rubbing her optics.  She 
opened a small thigh compartment and took out the last of her energon 
supply.  After breakfast, she continued to walk east.  She followed 
the mountain trail untill she finally came to the flat lands. She saw 
a great desert open up before her.  She saw the sunlight shine up 
from the white, sunbleached sand and earth. "How any bot can make it 
here is beyond me."  She looked at her scanner, but it was still 
fried.  She tried to use her commlink, but it wouldn't be able to 
recieve any transmissions. Only send.  She sat down on a stone and 
took out her small tool kit.  She figured she wasn't in a hurry to 
get anywhere, so she tried to fix her scanner and link. 
Unfortunately, she needed a few parts in order to fully repair them.  
So she would do the best she could and try to make them work if they 
would work at all.
